      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Local Open Scope pointed_scope.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** * [O]-connected covers *)\n\n(** Given a reflective subuniverse [O], for any type [X] and [x : O X], the [O]-connected cover of [X] at [x] is the fibre of [to O X] at [x]. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition O_cover@{u} `{O : ReflectiveSubuniverse@{u}}\n  (X : Type@{u}) (x : O X) : Type@{u}\n  := hfiber (to O _) x.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** The \"[O]-connected\" cover is in fact [O]-connected when [O] is a modality, using [isconnected_hfiber_conn_map]. Since Coq can infer this using typeclasses, we don't restate it here. *)\n\n(** Characterization of paths in [O_cover] is given by [equiv_path_hfiber]. *)\n\n(* If [x] is an actual point of [X], then the connected cover is pointed. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition O_pcover@{u} (O : ReflectiveSubuniverse@{u})\n  (X : Type@{u}) (x : X) : pType@{u}\n  := pfiber@{u u u} (pto O [X,x]).",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** Covers commute with products *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition O_pcover_prod `{O : ReflectiveSubuniverse} {X Y : pType@{u}}\n  : O_pcover O (X * Y) pt <~>* [(O_pcover O X pt) * (O_pcover O Y pt), _].",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": [
        {
          "_type": "goal",
          "name": null,
          "conclusion": "O_pcover O (X * Y) pt <~>* O_pcover O X pt * O_pcover O Y pt",
          "hypotheses": [
            {
              "_type": "hypothesis",
              "names": [
                "O"
              ],
              "body": null,
              "type": "ReflectiveSubuniverse"
            },
            {
              "_type": "hypothesis",
              "names": [
                "X",
                "Y"
              ],
              "body": null,
              "type": "pType"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
